你能够调用以下的API:
[['LeaseSearch.find_leases', {'name': 'LeaseSearch.find_leases', 'description': 'This function searches for lease agreements based on type and location.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'type', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The type of lease agreement, e.g., financial, real_estate.'}, {'name': 'location', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The location where the lease will be applied.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'leases', 'description': 'A list of up to three matching leases, each with an ID, type, and terms.'}]}], ['LeaseSearch.get_lease_details', {'name': 'LeaseSearch.get_lease_details', 'description': 'This function retrieves detailed information about a specific lease agreement given its ID.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'leaseId', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The ID of the lease agreement.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'details', 'description': 'Detailed information about the lease, including terms, conditions, and costs.'}]}], ['LeaseSearch.compare_leases', {'name': 'LeaseSearch.compare_leases', 'description': 'This function compares multiple lease agreements based on their IDs.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'leaseIds', 'type': 'ARRAY', 'description': 'An array of lease IDs to compare.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'comparison', 'description': 'A comparison of the selected leases, highlighting differences in terms and costs.'}]}], ['LegalSearch.find_laws', {'name': 'LegalSearch.find_laws', 'description': 'This function searches for laws and regulations based on topic and location.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'topic', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The topic of the law or regulation, e.g., financial_lease, real_estate.'}, {'name': 'location', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The location where the law applies.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'laws', 'description': 'A list of laws and regulations related to the topic and location.'}]}], ['MarketAnalysis.analyze_competition', {'name': 'MarketAnalysis.analyze_competition', 'description': 'This function analyzes the competitive landscape of a specific industry in a given location.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'industry', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The industry to analyze, e.g., financial_lease, technology.'}, {'name': 'location', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The location where the industry operates.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'analysis', 'description': 'An analysis of the competitive landscape, including major players, market share, and trends.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `LeaseSearch.find_leases` 并传入 `type` 和 `location`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "LeaseSearch.find_leases",
    "args": "{'type': 'financial', 'location': 'New York'}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
